name: Self portait, Line
description: I chose one of my favourite self portraits as my contribution to #OBJKT4OBJKT. To celebrate 10K (now 15K!) objects created on the platform. This one started out as sketch, but by the time I came to fill her in, I realised the look was already doing everything it needed. Free to 50 collectors. Find me on twitter for more: @studiojoprince
